  "original_title": "\u0db8\u0db8 \u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0da7 \u0dba\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0dda \u0dad\u0dd9\u0dbd\u0dca \u0d9c\u0dda\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0db1\u0dd9\u0db8\u0dd9\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "I am not going to Russia to bring oil",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Education Minister Susil Premjayant said that he had misunderstood his trip to France and that there is no opportunity to fly to Russia from any European country and there is no opportunity to come from Russia to any European country.",
        "He also said that as the President of Sri Lanka Russia - Parliamentary Friendship Association, he expects to visit Russia in the future to end the problematic situation between Russia and Sri Lanka.",
        "He also said that the problem situation related to Aeroflot Airline in Russia will be over after the case is taken in the court tomorrow.",
        "He also said that after the renewal of friendship, it will be possible to discuss issues such as energy and fertilizers with Russia in the future.",
        "He said that he is not going to Russia to bring oil but to update friendship."
      ],
